name: Screaming Monsters AAAAAAAAAA!
description:
Dia made this with her finger on iPhone using Adobe Fresco, I offered help for resizing and changing tools. Export as timelapse and attach audio via Adobe Rush. 

Little baby Dia is turning three next month on the 18th. We recently saw more kids on NFT and it's encouraging. Talking about doing fun activities with your child!

--

This project is a collaborative & learning platform between a tired mother and her (almost) 3 years old. Art, Crafts, and Music have always been her interest along with running around the house and climbing stuff. 

Support our journey into NFT by collecting our creations or connect with us via Twitter. We'd love to make some new friends <3
